## 1. Remove legal section from homepage
Deleted the 'Guest and host terms, right on the homepage' section
entirely from homepage-refresh.tsx. Terms/privacy/support remain
in the footer where they belong. Cleaned up now-unused Lock, Scale,
ShieldCheck lucide imports.

## 2. Fix Work Score 0/10 display
Score breakdown categories with score=0 now show 'Not assessed' in
grey italic instead of '0/10' with an orange bar. Added descriptive
tooltip to each category explaining what it measures and its max
points. Hovering any bar now shows the full context — useful for
both guests and hosts who want to understand the scoring.

## 3. Fix newsletter signup in footer
Extracted footer newsletter form to a client component (NewsletterForm).
On submit: POSTs to new /api/newsletter route, stores signup in
AnalyticsEvent table, optionally adds contact to Resend audience
(if RESEND_AUDIENCE_ID env var set). On success: shows inline
'You're in — we'll send deals your way.' confirmation with a green
checkmark. No more silent redirect to /register on submit.
