 =?UTF-8?q?=E2=80=94=20editorial=20luxury=20design=20system?=
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

## Design Direction
Refined editorial luxury: warm parchment base, Sahara gold accent,
terracotta CTAs, deep ink navy anchors. DM Sans body (replaces Inter),
Playfair Display headings, DM Mono for prices and scores.
Feels like Monocle magazine meets a premium travel brand.

## globals.css — complete rewrite
New palette: --ww-ink (#0d1f2d), --ww-gold (#c9a84c), --ww-gold-light,
--ww-celadon (#2d6a4f), --ww-parchment (#faf8f4), --ww-terra (#c17b4a),
--ww-mist (#e8e4dd), --ww-warm-white (#fffef9). All legacy --ww-primary-blue
etc aliased for backward compat.

Body: warm parchment with subtle radial gold/terra gradients + SVG noise
texture for tactile depth. Scrollbar, selection, focus ring all branded.

New utilities: ww-listing-card (hover lift + gold border glow),
ww-card-img-overlay (warm gradient), ww-score-badge (ink bg + gold text),
ww-eyebrow (celadon caps), ww-fade-up / ww-shimmer animations,
ww-header (warm glass blur), ww-hover-lift (spring cubic-bezier).

## layout.tsx
Font swap: Inter → DM Sans (more humanist and warm, not generic).
DM Mono added as --font-mono for prices and scores.
Playfair Display weight range extended to include 500.

## header.tsx
Full redesign: warm glass blur background, gold underline active state,
refined avatar menu with gold focus ring, mobile drawer with spring
animation. For Teams added to desktop nav. Cleaner auth buttons.

## footer.tsx
Warm gradient parchment background, three-column grid, eyebrow labels,
social icon buttons with gold hover. Editorial tone copy. Inline style
hover effects (no Tailwind hover needed for JS transitions).

## listing-card.tsx
Rebuilt without Card/Badge/CardContent primitives — pure semantic HTML.
ww-listing-card class with spring hover lift and gold border glow.
Score badge: ink background, gold/celadon/slate color by tier.
Price in DM Mono font. Mbps pill in celadon. 16:10 aspect ratio image.
Removed bed size (space recovery), added per-night label.

## home-hero.tsx
Full-bleed image with warm left-to-right + bottom-up overlay gradients.
Gold radial tint top-left as editorial signature. Parchment bottom fade
transitions cleanly to page background. Headline in large Playfair.
Gold-underlined 'work happens.' accent text. Trust pills with backdrop blur.
Terracotta CTA with terra glow shadow. Ghost secondary CTA with blur.
Min-height 88vh for dramatic full-screen presence.

## homepage-refresh.tsx
Featured listings: ww-listing-card pattern, score badge with tier colors,
price in monospace, celadon pilot badge, shimmer placeholders.
Browse categories: three solid-color cards (ink/celadon/terra) with
decorative circles and ArrowRight hover animation.
Host CTA: gold-light background, decorative large 'Host' background text,
ink CTA button with gold text — warm and premium.
