 =?UTF-8?q?=E2=80=94=20editorial=20luxury=20design=20system?=
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

## Design system overhaul (globals.css)
- New palette: ink navy (#0d1f2d), sahara gold (#c9a84c), celadon green
  (#2d6a4f), terracotta (#c17b4a), warm parchment (#faf8f4) — replaces
  flat blue/teal/orange with a warm, editorial, tactile palette
- Body background: warm parchment + radial gradient warmth + SVG noise
  grain at 2.5% opacity for subtle tactile depth
- Gold focus ring replacing blue — consistent brand colour on interaction
- Thin branded scrollbar: warm mist colour, invisible track
- Text selection uses gold-light — every touchpoint is branded

## Typography
- DM Sans replaces Inter — humanist, warm, less generic on screens
- DM Mono added for prices, scores, numbers — adds craft and precision
- Playfair Display weight range expanded: 400–800
- h1/h2/h3 use Playfair automatically via base layer
- Selection, scrollbar, focus-ring all branded

## New utility classes
- .ww-listing-card: spring-eased hover with gold border glow
- .ww-hover-lift: cubic-bezier spring lift on hover
- .ww-glass: frosted glass surface (header, modals)
- .ww-elevated: layered shadow for booking sidebar
- .ww-score-badge: ink bg + gold text — craft score display
- .ww-eyebrow: celadon all-caps section labels
- .ww-fade-up + delays: entry animations for hero elements
- .ww-shimmer: skeleton loading state
- .btn-primary / .btn-ghost: full brand-matched button styles
- .ww-input: warm-bordered input with gold focus ring
- .ww-card-img-overlay: editorial bottom gradient on card images
- .ww-gold-underline: animated gold decorative underline

## Header
- Rebuilt with glass blur effect (.ww-header)
- Active nav link gets gold underline indicator
- User menu: rounded pill with avatar, gold hover border
- Mobile drawer: ink-tinted overlay + slide-in nav
- CTA changed to terracotta 'Get started'

## BrandLogo
- New SVG mark: ink base + gold house with laptop symbol
- 'Way' in ink, 'Work' in gold — memorable split
- Refined tagline treatment in celadon

## Listing cards
- Full rebuild with ww-listing-card class
- Work Score badge: ink bg + gold number (monospace) — top-right
- Image overlay gradient — editorial bottom-to-top dark wash
- Verified badge in celadon, workspace type badge in parchment
- Connectivity stat with celadon badge + monospace number
- Match reasons in gold-light pills
- 'View →' terracotta link in footer row

## Property page
- Airbnb-style split gallery: 60/40 large+2 grid, 460px, rounded-2xl
- 'Show all photos' frosted glass button on third image
- Fast-read cards: parchment bg, gold-light amenity chips
- Quick facts: monospace values, celadon eyebrow labels
- Work Score breakdown: ink score tile, celadon/gold/terra bars
  matching score tier, parchment card backgrounds

## Booking sidebar
- Header gradient: ink to deep navy
- Date picker confirm button: ink bg
- Trust signals: celadon-light background
- Reserve CTA: terracotta

## Footer
- Parchment-to-warm gradient background
- Celadon eyebrow labels
- Social icon buttons with gold hover state
- Warm ♥ in terracotta in copyright bar

## Global token migration
- All 40 files migrated from ww-primary-blue/ww-secondary-green/
  ww-accent-orange/ww-text-primary to new palette
- Legacy aliases kept in :root for graceful fallback
