## Homepage cleanup
- Hero headline: 'Find beautiful spaces that work for work.'
- Removed browse categories section (Deep focus / Team stays / City escapes)
- Removed Host CTA blurb section from homepage body
- Header: added 'Become a host' ghost button between Log in and Get started
  → links to /become-a-host landing page, not directly to wizard
- Footer: stripped to 4 links only — About us, Terms, Privacy, Contact
  No newsletter, no social icons, no multi-column grid

## Become a host landing page (/become-a-host)
- Full host acquisition page with: hero + stat row (5–14 nights avg,
  12% commission, 48h payout, free to list), 6 benefit cards, 4-step
  how-it-works strip on ink background, what we look for checklist,
  transparent commission calculator card (€1,000 → €880 example),
  final CTA
- Commission breakdown: €1,000 guest payment → 12% → €880 host payout
- No blurb on homepage — all host context lives behind the button

## Booking confirmation page
- Rebuilt from scratch: celadon hero strip + overlapping white card
- Split photo + property details at top
- 2×2 stay details grid (check-in, check-out, duration, guests)
- Full pricing breakdown (subtotal, cleaning, total in monospace)
- Attendees list for team bookings
- Special requests block
- Celadon info strip (receipt emailed, message host, calendar invite)
- 3 action buttons: View booking, Message host, Add to calendar (.ics)
- .ics calendar file generated server-side for one-click calendar add

## Guest bookings dashboard (/bookings)
- Rebuilt as 'travel wallet' design: ink header band + overlapping cards
- Booking cards: image with countdown badge ('In 14d'), status pill,
  dates, nights, total in monospace, Leave review prompt for past stays
- Three sections: Upcoming (prominent), Past stays (with review CTA),
  Cancelled (collapsed if empty)
- Empty upcoming state shows Find a space CTA

## Host listings page (/host/listings)
- Rebuilt with ink header + card grid
- Each card: listing image, status pill (Active/Paused/Draft/In review),
  city, price/night, Work Score, active bookings count
- Quick actions: Edit, Preview (opens in new tab), Bookings filter
- Empty state with clear Create your first listing CTA
- Clean two-column layout (image left, details + actions right)
